| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3158 — Recovery Inhibition (coinbasecartel)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 58b42e44-2d81-5b94-91e1-55d4d88dc025"
